flowchart TD
    A[Input: User Preferences] --> B[Load songs.csv]
    B --> C[Loop through each song]
    C --> D[Compute categorical match<br/>Genre + Mood]
    D --> E[Compute numeric closeness<br/>Energy, Valence, Danceability,<br/>Tempo, Acousticness]
    E --> F[Combine into final score]
    F --> G[Store song + score]
    G --> H{More songs?}
    H -- Yes --> C
    H -- No --> I[Sort by score descending]
    I --> J[Output: Top K Recommendations]
